<paragraph id="IFRS01_30"><paranum>30</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 1"/><data name="paranum" value="30"/></prolog><body><variant base="F46425422" principles="no" id="IFRS01_30_V2">       <p id="IFRS01_P0138">If an entity uses <xref base="SL7282832" href="IFRS01_APPA.dita#IFRS01_APPA/IFRS01_DI0003" scope="local">fair value<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0119"/></ph></xref> in its <xref base="F7282735" href="IFRS01_APPA.dita#IFRS01_APPA/IFRS01_P0237">opening IFRS statement of financial position<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0267"/></ph></xref> as <xref base="F7282729" href="IFRS01_APPA.dita#IFRS01_APPA/IFRS01_P0224"><i>deemed cost</i><ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0074"/></ph></xref> for an item of property, plant and equipment, an investment property, an intangible asset or a right&#x2011;of&#x2011;use asset (see <xref base="F46425427" href="IFRS01_D5.dita#IFRS01_D5" id="IFRS01_X0213">paragraphs D5</xref> and <xref base="F46425428" href="IFRS01_D7.dita#IFRS01_D7" id="IFRS01_X0214">D7</xref>), the entity&#x2019;s first IFRS financial statements shall disclose, for each line item in the <xref base="F7282735" href="IFRS01_APPA.dita#IFRS01_APPA/IFRS01_P0237">opening IFRS statement of financial position<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0267"/></ph></xref>: </p>       <ol base="F46425430" type="lower-alpha" id="IFRS01_L0015"><li id="IFRS01_30_a"><li_value>(a)</li_value>           <p base="F46425432" id="IFRS01_P0139">the aggregate of those fair values; and</p>         </li><li id="IFRS01_30_b"><li_value>(b)</li_value>           <p base="F46425434" id="IFRS01_P0140">the aggregate adjustment to the carrying amounts reported under <xref base="F7282736" href="IFRS01_APPA.dita#IFRS01_APPA/IFRS01_P0239">previous GAAP<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0299"/></ph></xref>.</p>         </li></ol>     </variant></body></paragraph>